			<attribute id="needLayout" type="bool" value="False" />
			<attribute id="nextNodeId" type="uint32" value="112" />
			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="Post EA version of FOR_Village_OM_ShadowHeart_AOM_PostEA&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;After finding Sharan crown on a skeleton, an old journal speaking of local disappearances or a defiled statue of Selune, Shadowheart recognises that the ruined village of Moonhaven was attacked by Shar worshippers at some point and realises she may have allies nearby. While she's contemplating this, she experiences a flicker of strange magic. If present, her companions may notice this and ask what's the matter - she can be truthful or not, knowing that leading the party to a Shar stronghold could end in the deaths of some companions." />
